  <?dbhtml filename="libxfixes.html"?>

  <title>libXfixes-&libxfixes-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      libXfixes provides an X Window System client interface to the 'XFIXES'
      extension to the X protocol.
    </para>

